67
0:03:26.074,000 --> 0:03:28,000
And you just feel the anger and you feel the fear.

68
0:03:29.634,000 --> 0:03:31,000
If you can, that's empathy. That's empathy.

69
0:03:32.424,000 --> 0:03:35,000
You've left your shoes, and you've stood in mine.

70
0:03:36.398,000 --> 0:03:37,000
And you've got to feel that.

71
0:03:38.237,000 --> 0:03:39,000
OK, so that's the warm-up.

72
0:03:40.316,000 --> 0:03:41,000
That's the warm-up.

73
0:03:41.512,000 --> 0:03:44,000
